<br>
Every server has different names for the giants so I am gonna give directions the best I can.<br>
<br>
Enter BoT.<br>
Run up the steps.<br>
Continue straight from the steps up the ramp into the "Water" giant area.<br>
Take your first left and run up the slope.<br>
In the first room you come to there will be a xxxx Kriger.<br>
The Kriger is the PH for the namer who drops the gauntlets.<br>
The namer is the EXACT same name as the Upper (tower) boss.  Eindrede Icestorm (spelling prolly off).<br>
<br>
Out of 60-70 kills of this namer we got 3 pairs of gauntlets.  He is decently rare and the gauntlets used to be really rare.  I havent really played in BoT in almost 3 months now, but this is where I got them and the approx drop rates.<br>
<br>
Hope this helps.<br>
